{"tid":1801682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係想分化，但可唔可以唔好上裝然後企撚左係度","createTime":"2019-12-28T21:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T02:28:17.000Z","uid":23046,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c978f4a88adb790bbcd7b4833b8e187331ecbd7f","tid":1801682,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T21:20:43.000Z","msg":"今日德福果幾個係想點<br />\n係呀，你可以話班狗亂捉<br />\n但一撚定係target啲有罩bb先架囉<br />\n如果你話便衣<br />\n屌佢地其實都係一群咁走出黎<br />\n好易就睇到，仲要啲記者已經圍哂佢地幫手擋住<br />\n我當你都係分唔到見唔到邊啲係狗<br />\n咁係咪更唔應該企左係度<br />\n跟住你地比人逗，其他手足就去救<br />\n跟住全軍覆沒<br />\n究竟係想點？<br />\n唔係一個位一個手足<br />\n而係幾個位都有人係咁<br />\n<br />\n唔該靜左未做野就搵時間去番廁所換裝啦<br />\n再做野先換番裝<br />\n<br />\nbe water呀大佬"},{"pid":"b61cad8e7155bfe05d10732880893c5335d87a58","tid":1801682,"uid":98993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T21:22:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22eccb8a902f36342a72cddb079c1572effcfae8","tid":1801682,"uid":23046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T21:24:21.000Z","msg":"難聽啲講<br />\n上左裝企當眼位唔郁<br />\n同送頭冇分別<br />\n仲要搞到其他人去救你<br />\n<br />\n唔好咁搞啦<br />\n你可能個身冇野唔怕<br />\n但其他手足唔知架<br />\n佢地會去救你<br />\n跟住佢地死撚硬"},{"pid":"f8240ac4350dbfab3c9db97269442efd063bb934","tid":1801682,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T02:27:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a27176cd0f745375d8714d9a69b71dcd91cebc63","tid":1801682,"uid":54921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T02:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借個位黎用下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">由窮爸爸富爸爸探討黃色經濟圈發展</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1801758/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://l